      <abstract>
        <p>Roundup of recent advertising account changes (Advertising column) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Bissell Inc., Grand Rapids, Mich., to Campbell-Ewald, Warren, Mich., part of the Interpublic Group of Cos., to handle the account of the appliance maker, which had been at Tom Reilly Advertising, Evanston, Ill. Billings were estimated at $20 million.</p>
